data.description: Welcome to your new home! This two story condo is located in the beautiful and quiet community of Iris Landing. The gated community sits at the heart of Rancho Belago, and upscale and newer part of Moreno Valley. This 1544 square foot condo home boasts a spacious 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with an attached 2 car garage. On the first floor you’ll find the living room, dining room, and a large kitchen with recess lighting and granite countertops-perfect for hosting guest and entertaining! As an added bonus, on the first level you’ll also find a half bath, a designated room for washer and dryer, and direct access to the garage. All three bedrooms are located on the second floor, two of which have walk in closets with ample space!  There are two full bathrooms located upstairs,  one located in the luxe owner’s suite. Enjoy your morning coffee in your sizable front porch, large enough for a you to set up a relaxing sitting area, try your hand at pot gardening, or enjoy some outdoor yoga!     This home is also conveniently located at walking distance from Kaiser Permanente, Stater Brothers, Starbucks, Juice It Up, banks, and more!
